  "category": "generative",
  "url": "shaders/gen-holographic-rainbow-surface.wgsl",
  "description": "A liquid holographic surface with iridescent rainbow colors that ripple and undulate like liquid light. Prismatic diffraction highlights, spectral color separation based on surface normals, and mouse-reactive wave propagation create a stunning chromatic light simulation.",
